learning_outcomes.en:
After completing the course, students:
- can come up with a feasible and relevant linguistics research question within Finno-Ugric linguistics;
- can choose a suitable corpus and extract the necessary data from the corpus;
- can use language technology and concordancing tools to advance their research;
- are aware of the ethical and legal issues involved;
- understand the basics of statistical testing
- complete a basic research project using corpus data
